name: ANTPARK TOKEN
description: Ant Park is an aggregated meta universe cultivation game based on BSC Smart Chain. It uses blockchain technology to create a meta universe ecological game that can break common problems in the industry. In Ant Park, all players will enter a new world, everything is new, waiting for players everywhere to unify the world. Ant Park adopts the community voting system. In the future, every player may become a rule maker and the founder of the country. All players can have a real immersive experience virtual space.
